   I found the pagan witch and stole a amulet from her but I got caught.
  '- This amulet is cursed, you foolish man!' - said the witch, '- It must remain hidden for all time, guarded by a sea of lava. Hang him! ' - she said, pointing at me.

  I pulled free of the shaggy bandit's grasp and tried to flee, but something terrible slammed into my back and burned along my entire body. I managed to escape but I'm too weak to go any farther..."
